short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Create new sets from your starred terms with the click of a button!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With SelectiveStudy for Quizlet, you can make a new Quizlet set from your flashcards with ease.

Features:
- Make a new set with starred terms automatically, text only
- Preserve term and definition languages

Planned updates:
- Support for images
- Automatically generate title
